- **Your Guide**: `workflow/CODEX_GUIDE.md` (detailed instructions)
- **Design Spec**: `workflow/steps/step2_design.md` (implementation plan)
- **Architecture**: `workflow/architecture.md` (system overview)
- **Testing**: `workflow/testing-playbook.md` (test commands)
- **Full Rules**: `workflow/COLLABORATION_GUIDE.md` (complete workflow)

## 🔧 Quick Commands

```bash
# Check current step
cat workflow/state/current_step.json

# Read design
cat workflow/steps/step2_design.md

# Run tests
python3.11 -m pytest -q

# Log progress
echo "- $(date +%H:%M) [Codex] Did X" >> workflow/progress.md

# Mark completed
jq '.status = "completed" | .owner = "claude"' workflow/state/current_step.json > tmp && mv tmp workflow/state/current_step.json
```

## 🎯 Remember

1. **Design First**: Never code without reading `step2_design.md`
2. **Test Always**: After each file, run tests
3. **Document Everything**: Update `progress.md` continuously

**Good luck! 🚀**
